  <p>Privacy requests: <a href="mailto:privacy@abelost.com">privacy@abelost.com</a><br />Legal notices: <a href="mailto:legal@abelost.com">legal@abelost.com</a></p>
  <p>Abelost is an online-first project and does not provide estimates or support by telephone.</p>
</ContentLayout>
